    "encrypted": "false",
    "long_instructions": "## Historical Event\r\n\r\nUse AI Chat to analyze a historical image alongside a primary source document.\r\n\r\n### Do This:\r\n\r\n1. **Choose an Image**: Select one of the **provided historical** images or upload an image of a historical event relevant to you.\r\n2. **Select a Historical Document**: Choose one of the **provided primary source PDFs** to give additional context to your analysis.\r\n3. **Upload Both the Image & the Document**: Attach the selected historical image and corresponding PDF to AI Chat.\r\n4. **Copy and paste** the following prompt:\r\n\r\n>Analyze this image and document together. What does the image reveal about this historical event? How does the document provide additional context? How might AI interpret the event differently depending on which source is provided?\r\n\r\n5. **Experiment and Compare:**\r\n   - First, ask AI to analyze the image alone. Then, add the document and see how its response changes.\r\n   - Modify your prompt to ask AI for a summary vs. a detailed analysis. Compare the responses.\r\n   - Test different AI-generated outputs:\r\n      - Ask AI to generate a newspaper headline based on the image alone.\r\n      - Then, ask for a headline based on both the image and document.\r\n      - How does the added context influence AI’s response?\r\n   \r\n   \r\n---\r\n\r\n**Questions to Consider:**\r\n- What key details does AI focus on in the image?\r\n- How does AI’s response change when given the historical document?\r\n- Does AI accurately interpret the document, or does it misrepresent details?\r\n- How would a historian analyze these sources differently?",
